Featuring @kylecease 
In this sketch video, a naive man wonders into the MK Ultra office, wanting to become an asset because he just wants to serve his country. The MK Ultra agent, who’s dark and sinister agendas are completely covered by a charming upbeat facade, then leads the candidate through an impromptu interview process. The interview involves the candidate being indoctrinated into torture based mind control and then activation to test if he is controllable enough to be an MK Ultra asset.
